er&apos;s</span> <span begin="23.871" end="25.788">day)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在一个冬日里</span></span></p><p begin="25.228" end="30.558" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.228" end="25.547">I&apos;d</span> <span begin="25.547" end="25.774">be</span> <span begin="25.774" end="26.058">safe</span> <span begin="26.058" end="26.294">and</span> <span begin="26.294" end="27.578">warm</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我会安全又温暧</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="26.293" end="30.558"><span begin="26.293" end="26.844">(I&apos;d</span> <span begin="26.844" end="27.344">be</span> <span begin="27.344" end="27.681">safe</span> <span begin="27.681" end="28.242">and</span> <span begin="28.242" end="30.558">warm)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我会安全又温暧</span></span></p><p begin="29.004" end="34.094" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.004" end="29.301">If</span> <span begin="29.301" end="29.544">I</span> <span begin="29.544" end="29.801">was</span> <span begin="29.801" end="30.097">in</span> <span begin="30.097" end="31.121">L A</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果这是在洛杉矶</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="31.121" end="34.094"><span begin="31.121" end="31.427">(If</span> <span begin="31.427" end="31.684">I</span> <span begin="31.684" end="31.956">was</span> <span begin="31.956" end="32.217">in</span> <span begin="32.217" end="34.094">L A)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果这是在洛杉矶</span></span></p><p begin="33.829" end="37.934" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="33.829" end="34.895">California</span> <span begin="34.895" end="37.919">dreaming</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">加州梦</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="34.911" end="37.934"><span begin="34.911" end="36.762">(California</span> <span begin="36.762" end="37.934">dreaming)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">加州梦</span></span></p><p begin="37.924" end="42.202" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.924" end="38.106">On</span> <span begin="38.106" end="38.358">such</span> <span begin="38.358" end="38.640">a</span> <span begin="38.640" end="39.149">winter&apos;s</span> <span begin="39.149" end="41.034">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在这样的冬日升起</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="37.924" end="42.202"><span begin="37.924" end="38.106">(On</span> <span begin="38.106" end="38.358">such</span> <span begin="38.358" end="38.640">a</span> <span begin="38.640" end="39.149">winter&apos;s</span> <span begin="39.149" end="42.202">day)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在这样的冬日升起</span></span></p><p begin="42.202" end="43.960" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.202" end="42.585">Stopped</span> <span begin="42.585" end="42.976">into</span> <span begin="42.976" end="43.132">a</span> <span begin="43.132" end="43.960">church</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">停车走进教堂</span></p><p begin="45.833" end="48.305" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="45.833" end="46.159">I</span> <span begin="46.159" end="46.514">passed</span> <span begin="46.514" end="47.469">along</span> <span begin="47.469" end="47.726">the</span> <span begin="47.726" end="48.305">way</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我穿过走道</span></p><p begin="50.099" end="56.393" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.099" end="50.543">Well</span> <span begin="50.543" end="50.942">I</span> <span begin="50.942" end="51.167">got</span> <span begin="51.167" end="51.477">down</span> <span begin="51.477" end="51.733">on</span> <span begin="51.733" end="52.044">my</span> <span begin="52.044" end="53.292">knees</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我跪了下来</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="51.998" end="56.393"><span begin="51.998" end="52.552">(Got</span> <span begin="52.552" end="53.055">down</span> <span begin="53.055" end="53.384">on</span> <span begin="53.384" end="53.906">my</span> <span begin="53.906" end="56.393">knees)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">跪了下来</span></span></p><p begin="54.420" end="59.983" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="54.420" end="54.683">And</span> <span begin="54.683" end="54.870">I</span> <span begin="54.870" end="55.706">pretend</span> <span begin="55.706" end="55.981">to</span> <span begin="55.981" end="56.802">pray</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">然后我假装祈祷</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="56.802" end="59.983"><span begin="56.802" end="57.075">(I</span> <span begin="57.075" end="57.880">pretend</span> <span begin="57.880" end="58.137">to</span> <span begin="58.137" end="59.983">pray)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我假装祈祷</span></span></p><p begin="58.687" end="1:04.727" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="58.687" end="58.925">You</span> <span begin="58.925" end="59.231">know</span> <span begin="59.231" end="59.493">the</span> <span begin="59.493" end="59.979">preacher</span> <span begin="59.979" end="1:00.251">likes</span> <span begin="1:00.251" end="1:00.519">the</span> <span begin="1:00.519" end="1:01.366">cold</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你知道牧师喜欢寒冷</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:00.522" end="1:04.727"><span begin="1:00.522" end="1:01.615">(Preacher</span> <span begin="1:01.615" end="1:02.135">likes</span> <span begin="1:02.135" end="1:02.420">the</span> <span begin="1:02.420" end="1:04.727">cold)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">牧师喜欢寒冷</span></span></p><p begin="1:02.933" end="1:08.746" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.933" end="1:03.240">He</span> <span begin="1:03.240" end="1:03.772">knows</span> <span begin="1:03.772" end="1:04.093">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:04.093" end="1:04.775">gonna</span> <span begin="1:04.775" end="1:05.403">stay</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他知道我会留下来</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:05.403" end="1:08.746"><span begin="1:05.403" end="1:05.658">(Knows</span> <span begin="1:05.658" end="1:05.937">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="1:05.937" end="1:06.622">gonna</span> <span begin="1:06.622" end="1:08.746">stay)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">知道我会留下来</span></span></p><p begin="1:08.064" end="1:12.089" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:08.064" end="1:09.167">California</span> <span begin="1:09.167" end="1:12.089">dreaming</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">加州梦</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:09.184" end="1:12.089"><span begin="1:09.184" end="1:11.003">(California</span> <span begin="1:11.003" end="1:12.089">dreaming)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">加州梦</span></span></p><p begin="1:12.089" end="1:16.665" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.089" end="1:12.296">On</span> <span begin="1:12.296" end="1:12.562">such</span> <span begin="1:12.562" end="1:12.810">a</span> <span begin="1:12.810" end="1:13.394">winter&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:13.394" end="1:16.010">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在这样的冬日</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:12.089" end="1:16.665"><span begin="1:12.089" end="1:12.296">(On</span> <span begin="1:12.296" end="1:12.562">such</span> <span begin="1:12.562" end="1:12.810">a</span> <span begin="1:12.810" end="1:13.394">winter&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:13.394" end="1:16.665">day)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在这样的冬日</span></span></p><p begin="1:50.457" end="1:55.646" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:50.457" end="1:50.701">All</span> <span begin="1:50.701" end="1:50.985">the</span> <span begin="1:50.985" end="1:51.230">leaves</span> <span begin="1:51.230" end="1:51.468">are</span> <span begin="1:51.468" end="1:52.546">brown</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">树叶转黄</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:51.471" end="1:55.646"><span begin="1:51.471" end="1:52.022